A vibrant, slightly chaotic illustration of a towering, ornate, ancient-looking enchantment—a swirling, aged bronze goblet overflowing with iridescent, bubbling potion—surrounding a group of powerfully animated, slightly staggered, and drunken human warriors, all trampling forward with furious expressions, rendered in a painterly, slightly distressed style reminiscent of old stained glass windows, 2025 art, magical realism.